victims_database.prompt_for_victim_tweets:
Generate a tweet honoring this victim.

VICTIM INFO:
Name: {{name}}
Age: {{age}}
City: {{city}}
Circumstances: {{circumstances}}
Occupation: {{occupation}}

RULES:
1. Dignified, not exploitative
2. Humanize without sensationalizing
3. Include name prominently
4. Keep factual
5. End with call to remember, not just rage

OUTPUT: A single tweet that honors their memory while advancing the cause.
